OL,3,C'Like tomato soup': Why did river turn
OL,4,Corange?
OL,6,FWitnesses have described the River
OL,7,FCalder in West Yorkshire as resembling
OL,8,F"tomato soup" after it turned a bright
OL,9,Forange colour.
OL,11,FPictures and videos posted on social
OL,12,Fmedia showed the river flowing a
OL,13,Fvibrant colour on Thursday, 24
OL,14,FOctober, with some describing its
OL,15,Fappearance as "insane".
OL,17,FIt is not the first time water courses
OL,18,Fin the area have been discoloured.
OL,20,FSimilar events occurred in both 2014
OL,21,Fand 2022.
