OL,3,C'Like tomato soup': Why did river turn
OL,4,Corange?
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency said it had
OL,7,Fsent officers to investigate the
OL,8,Fsource of the issue.
OL,10,FWhy does the river turn orange?
OL,12,FDespite tongue-in-cheek speculation
OL,13,Fthat there had been a serious tomato
OL,14,Fsoup leak, or that thousands of litres
OL,15,Fof Iron Bru had somehow found their
OL,16,Fway into the river, the explanation is
OL,17,Fmuch more mundane.
