OL,3,C'Like tomato soup': Why did river turn
OL,4,Corange?
OL,6,FA number of social media users were
OL,7,Fquick to point out the correct reason,
OL,8,Fidentifying disused mines as the
OL,9,Fsource.
OL,11,FIn a Facebook post, Elaine Horsted
OL,12,Fwrote: "It's iron from the hill
OL,13,Fwater... It's always happened when
OL,14,Fwe've had a lot of hill water from the
OL,15,Fold mines up there."
OL,17,FDave Halley added: "Last time it went
OL,18,Fdown the road and dyed all the
OL,19,Froadside house's orange to about 4ft
OL,20,Ffor a couple of miles."
