OL,3,C'Like tomato soup': Why did river turn
OL,4,Corange?
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency confirmed as
OL,7,Fmuch, in a post on X.
OL,9,FA spokesperson said: "We've received
OL,10,Freports about the River Calder turning
OL,11,Fbright orange in Todmorden, which is
OL,12,Fdue to water escaping from old mines.
OL,14,F"Officers are investigating the
OL,15,Fsource, but we don't expect any
OL,16,Fsignificant or long-term water quality
OL,17,Fissues."
OL,19,FThe agency is not expected to take any
OL,20,Ffurther action, with the colour
OL,21,Freturning to normal in due course.
